  <name>Cosmic Pomodoro</name>
  <summary>Simple Pomodoro applet for COSMIC Desktop</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Cosmic Pomodoro is a minimal and distraction-free Pomodoro applet for
      the COSMIC desktop.
    </p>
    <p>
      It provides configurable work, short break, and long break intervals,
      panel integration, localized UI, and subtle notifications.
    </p>
  </description>
  <icon type="stock">io.github.petar030.cosmic-pomodoro</icon>
